snippet.title: Welcome to the Game 2+ Mod - Update v1.3 Trailer
snippet.description:
Teaser Trailer to the newest 1.3 update to the WTTG2+ mod that adds new items, websites and a new enemy, the Bomb Maker.

The Welcome to the Game 2+ Mod is a fanmade project that adds several new gameplay mechanics to the game, these are:
- Fully fletched out Twitch Integration
- New Websites
- New Enemies
- New Items
- and much more

If you want to give it a shot yourself, check out my friend's Discord Server for instructions: https://discord.gg/fxCSKdW

KotzwurstPro 2021
